g&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-gr-google_analytics-enabled&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;gr:google_analytics:enabled&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;true&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-gr-fb_pixel-enabled&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;gr:fb_pixel:enabled&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;true&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-gr-tiktok_pixel-enabled&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;gr:tiktok_pixel:enabled&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;true&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-gr-logged_in_user-id&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;gr:logged_in_user:id&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-gr-page-type&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;gr:page:type&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;product&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-name-description&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;description&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;You raised, shipped, or bootstrapped your product - but ask you for your real MRR, churn, CAC, LTV or runway right now and the honest answer is a shrug and a messy spreadsheet. Founders lose money and miss raises not because the business is bad, but because they cannot see the numbers clearly. Cobbling formulas together at midnight before an investor call is no way to run a company.This SaaS Metrics \u0026amp; Startup Financial Model fixes that. Type your subscription data into clearly marked cells and the workbook instantly calculates every metric that matters - MRR, ARR, growth, churn, CAC, LTV, LTV:CAC, payback, net burn and runway - and projects the next 36 months from your own assumptions. Every formula is real and visible, so you (and your investors) can trust the maths.WHAT&#39;S INSIDE (10 tabs):1. Instructions - a clear walkthrough and how to import into Google Sheets.2. Dashboard - every headline KPI plus charts, pulled live from the other tabs.3. Assumptions - one control panel; edit the highlighted input cells, everything else updates.4. Subscriptions / MRR - log new, expansion, contraction and churned MRR; net \u0026amp; end MRR auto.5. Revenue - recurring plus one-time revenue, monthly total and implied ARR.6. Expenses - costs by category (salaries, infrastructure, marketing, tools, other).7. CAC \u0026amp; LTV - CAC, ARPA, gross-margin LTV, the LTV:CAC ratio and CAC payback in months.8. Cohort Retention - monthly cohorts with an automatic retention % table.9. Runway \u0026amp; Burn - cash in vs out, net burn, ending cash and months of runway left.10. 3-Year Projection - 36 months of MRR, ARR, customers, expenses and cash, plus a chart.WHY YOU&#39;LL LOVE IT:- Real, visible formulas - verify the maths yourself; nothing is hard-coded or faked.- Works in Excel, Google Sheets and Apple Numbers - no add-ons, no account, no install.- Input cells are colour-coded so you always know exactly what to fill in.- Comes pre-filled with example data so it makes sense the moment you open it - clear it and add yours.- A START HERE guide gets you to your real numbers in about 10 minutes.- Instant download - nothing ships.Stop guessing your numbers. Open the workbook, enter your data, and see your whole business on one screen. Instant download.(Single-user licence - use it for all of your own companies and projects. Please do not resell or redistribute.)&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-product-retailer_item_id&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;product:retailer_item_id&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;jxravw&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-product-price-amount&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;product:price:amount&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:29.0},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-product-price-currency&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;product:price:currency&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;USD&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-og-description&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;og:description&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;You raised, shipped, or bootstrapped your product - but ask you for your real MRR, churn, CAC, LTV or runway right now and the honest answer is a shrug and a messy spreadsheet. Founders lose money and miss raises not because the business is bad, but because they cannot see the numbers clearly. Cobbling formulas together at midnight before an investor call is no way to run a company.This SaaS Metrics \u0026amp; Startup Financial Model fixes that. Type your subscription data into clearly marked cells and the workbook instantly calculates every metric that matters - MRR, ARR, growth, churn, CAC, LTV, LTV:CAC, payback, net burn and runway - and projects the next 36 months from your own assumptions. Every formula is real and visible, so you (and your investors) can trust the maths.WHAT&#39;S INSIDE (10 tabs):1. Instructions - a clear walkthrough and how to import into Google Sheets.2. Dashboard - every headline KPI plus charts, pulled live from the other tabs.3. Assumptions - one control panel; edit the highlighted input cells, everything else updates.4. Subscriptions / MRR - log new, expansion, contraction and churned MRR; net \u0026amp; end MRR auto.5. Revenue - recurring plus one-time revenue, monthly total and implied ARR.6. Expenses - costs by category (salaries, infrastructure, marketing, tools, other).7. CAC \u0026amp; LTV - CAC, ARPA, gross-margin LTV, the LTV:CAC ratio and CAC payback in months.8. Cohort Retention - monthly cohorts with an automatic retention % table.9. Runway \u0026amp; Burn - cash in vs out, net burn, ending cash and months of runway left.10. 3-Year Projection - 36 months of MRR, ARR, customers, expenses and cash, plus a chart.WHY YOU&#39;LL LOVE IT:- Real, visible formulas - verify the maths yourself; nothing is hard-coded or faked.- Works in Excel, Google Sheets and Apple Numbers - no add-ons, no account, no install.- Input cells are colour-coded so you always know exactly what to fill in.- Comes pre-filled with example data so it makes sense the moment you open it - clear it and add yours.- A START HERE guide gets you to your real numbers in about 10 minutes.- Instant download - nothing ships.Stop guessing your numbers. Open the workbook, enter your data, and see your whole business on one screen. Instant download.(Single-user licence - use it for all of your own companies and projects. Please do not resell or redistribute.)&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-og-url&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;og:url&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;https://planfulnest.gumroad.com/l/jxravw&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-og-type&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;og:type&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;gumroad:product&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-twitter-title&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;twitter:title&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;SaaS Metrics \u0026 Startup Financial Model Spreadsheet — MRR&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-twitter-card&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;twitter:card&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;summary_large_image&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-twitter-image&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;twitter:image&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;https://public-files.gumroad.com/s8cqyvos1htzacj3ubsnlplysvoq&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-twitter-image-alt&quot;,&quot;property&quot;:&quot;twitter:image:alt&quot;},{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;meta&quot;,&quot;headKey&quot;:&quot;meta-property-twitter-domain&quot